00:01:38.435 --> 00:01:42.195
in your backlog and lastly the section, initiative-driven Project Backlog.

33
00:01:42.195 --> 00:01:43.878
To me the most critical,

34
00:01:43.878 --> 00:01:47.185
important and strategic project should be initiative-driven.

35
00:01:47.185 --> 00:01:50.833
Sure there will be projects coming from operations or other parts of the

